body_html:

Although while building Tensorflow 1.8.0 build fails with following error

ERROR: /home/test/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco/python/BUILD:22:1: Linking of rule '//tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco/python:_tensorflow_wrap_toco.so' failed (Exit 1)
gcc: error: tensorflow_wrap_toco_versionscript.lds: No such file or directory

gcc version:

test@3df991c9ea6c:~/tensorflow$ gcc --version
gcc (Ubuntu 7.3.0-16ubuntu3) 7.3.0

warranty; not even for MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.

Although while building Tensorflow 1.8.0 build fails with following error 
```
ERROR: /home/test/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco/python/BUILD:22:1: Linking of rule '//tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco/python:_tensorflow_wrap_toco.so' failed (Exit 1)
gcc: error: tensorflow_wrap_toco_versionscript.lds: No such file or directory
```
gcc version:
```
test@3df991c9ea6c:~/tensorflow$ gcc --version
gcc (Ubuntu 7.3.0-16ubuntu3) 7.3.0
Copyright (C) 2017 Free Software Foundation, Inc.
This is free software; see the source for copying conditions.  There is NO
warranty; not even for MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.
```

Any specific version of gcc to be used?
